Address: New York, NY
Rules:
{
  "jurisdiction": "new york",
  "building_permit": true,
  "electrical_permit": true,

parsed_form.friendly_notes: new york typically requires building_permit, electrical_permit with an average review time of 10 days and a fire code setback of 18 inches.
